<li><a href="http://www.thebulletin.org" class="external text" title="http://www.thebulletin.org" rel="nofollow">Bulletin of the Atomic Scientists</a> - A non-technical public policy and global security magazine that has reported on nuclear proliferation issues since 1945.</li>
